  "comment": {
    "text": "This text appears in a confirmation dialog for tool calls. It informs the user that the platform cannot guarantee the security practices of the integrated third-party tool, providing a disclaimer related to data shared with that tool. It's crucial for translators to convey this limitation of responsibility.",
